observation: On May 25th, @FrankGrimes was observed to perform to a good standard. This was evidenced by his work in the cafeteria, where he showed #teamwork #initiative. He worked well with the other employees, efficiently preparing food and cleaning up. When Homer Simpson accidentally spilled a tray of food, Frank quickly helped clean it up and joked with Homer about his clumsiness, displaying #humor #camaraderie.
